 	 * (MIGRATE_CMA).
 	 *
+	 * pages_with_online_memmap is pages within the zone that have an online
+	 * memmap. It includes present pages and memory holes that have a memmap.
+	 * When spanned_pages == pages_with_online_memmap, pfn_to_page() can be
