```

Okay, the issue is that `zone_end_pfn(zone)` calculates the end of the zone as `zone->zone_start_pfn + zone->spanned_pages`. In the case where `zone->zone_start_pfn == start_pfn`, the function first updates `spanned_pages` and then updates `zone->zone_start_pfn`. Critically, `WRITE_ONCE` is used on `spanned_pages`, but not on `zone_start_pfn`.

